observations.recommendation:
We recommended the Management to:
Create an item for General Services Officer to maintain a Local Road Network Inventory and Road Map and to keep a complete Local Road Network Property Card for all roads and its components;
Inform the Municipal Treasurer to periodically render Report of Local Road Networks, and furnish copies to the concerned offices. Also, Municipal Engineer’s Office should provide the Municipal Accountant and the Property Officer with the complete description and cost segregation of road components for road projects;
Require the Municipal Accountant to maintain a separate subsidiary ledger for each individual road networks; and
Ensure coordination among LGU Offices to properly implement the accounting and reporting guidelines on the Local Road Asset Management System.
